She thinks you're nice</i>

36:01.987 --> 36:04.656
<i>Got what it takes to go to paradise</i>

36:04.740 --> 36:07.368
<i>She likes your face
Said she likes your rig</i>

36:07.451 --> 36:10.412
<i>But, man, oh, man
Them things are too big</i>

36:10.496 --> 36:11.705
<i>Your feet's too big</i>

