1:09:37.878 --> 1:09:41.173
<i>Break another little piece
Of my heart, yeah, darling</i>

1:09:42.007 --> 1:09:43.342
<i>Oh, have a...!</i>

1:09:43.425 --> 1:09:47.345
<i>Have another little piece
Of my heart, yeah, baby</i>

1:09:48.347 --> 1:09:53.477
<i>You know you got it
If it makes you feel good</i>

1:09:55.688 --> 1:09:57.940
All right. I see you!

1:09:59.149 --> 1:09:59.983
There you go.

1:10:01.276 --> 1:10:02.111
Yeah.

1:10:02.778 --> 1:10:03.612
Look here.

1:10:04.154 --> 1:10:06.365
<i>I'mma need you to come on</i>

1:10:06.448 --> 1:10:08.117
No. No, thank you.

1:10:08.200 --> 1:10:10.703
<i>Come on, come on</i>

1:10:10.786 --> 1:10:11.954
<i>And take it!</i>

1:10:12.037 --> 1:10:15.666
<i>Take another little piece
